videos.headline: C.J. Stroud threads the needle to Chris Olave for Ohio State TD
videos.description: Ohio State QB C.J. Stroud slings a 23-yard touchdown pass to Chris Olave to give the Buckeyes the early lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (C.J. Stroud threads the needle to Chris Olave for Ohio State TD) 2021/11/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Buckeyes' fans erupt as C.J. Stroud finds Garrett Wilson for 77-yard TD
videos.description: Ohio State QB C.J. Stroud finds Garrett Wilson in stride for a 77-yard touchdown play to widen the Buckeyes' lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Buckeyes' fans erupt as C.J. Stroud finds Garrett Wilson for 77-yard TD) 2021/11/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Buckeyes' Chris Olave gets second TD reception of the day
videos.description: Ohio State QB C.J. Stroud flings a 43-yard touchdown to Chris Olave, their second TD connection of the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Buckeyes' Chris Olave gets second TD reception of the day) 2021/11/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: C.J. Stroud tosses fourth TD of the first half for Ohio State
videos.description: Ohio State QB C.J. Stroud finds Julian Fleming for a touchdown, adding to Stroud's stellar first half vs. Michigan State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (C.J. Stroud tosses fourth TD of the first half for Ohio State) 2021/11/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Chris Olave's spectacular grab sets up another Buckeyes TD
videos.description: Ohio State WR Chris Olave makes an incredible catch along the sidelines and on the next play, Miyan Williams punches it in for an Ohio State score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Chris Olave's spectacular grab sets up another Buckeyes TD) 2021/11/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: C.J. Stroud pours it on with fifth TD pass for Ohio State
videos.description: Ohio State QB C.J. Stroud throws a 12-yard touchdown pass to Garrett Wilson to increase the Buckeyes' lead to 42-0 over Michigan State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (C.J. Stroud pours it on with fifth TD pass for Ohio State) 2021/11/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Stroud connects with Smith-Njigba for his sixth TD pass of the game
videos.description: Ohio State QB C.J. Stroud flips a five-yard touchdown pass to Jaxon Smith-Njigba, giving Stroud his sixth TD of the first half.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Stroud connects with Smith-Njigba for his sixth TD pass of the game) 2021/11/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: C.J. Stroud lights up for 6 first-half TDs for Ohio State
videos.description: Ohio State QB C.J. Stroud was near perfect in the first half as he tosses for 393 yards and six touchdowns.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (C.J. Stroud lights up for 6 first-half TDs for Ohio State) 2021/11/20 ESHHET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Michigan State finally gets on the board after Keon Coleman's TD catch
videos.description: Michigan State QB Payton Thorne lobs it to Keon Coleman in the end zone for a 12-yard score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Michigan State finally gets on the board after Keon Coleman's TD catch) 2021/11/20 ESHEET
